A personal attempt to create a web project that includes a frontpage,
a blog and some more cool stuff. It's written in Python and by using
django framework.

REQUIREMENTS
----------------

* django (>= 1.1)
* python-imaging
* django-tagging
* django-registration (optional)
* django-profiles (optional)
* python-openid (optional)
* python-*sql (optional when using sqlite)
* BeautifulSoup (optional when using colorizing)
* python-twitter (optional)

NOTES ON DEPLOYMENT
-----------------------

* /media/admin/ should be linked to django's admin media folder
* you can overwrite any setting by creating settings in local_settings.py (you need to create it first)
* /favicon.ico should be an alias to /media/images/favicon.png
